OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776359147
OL,3,COily paint leaks onto road after fly-
OL,4,Ctippers dump containers in Dorset
OL,6,FFly-tippers have caused "significant"
OL,7,Fdamage and risked the local
OL,8,Fenvironment after dumping containers
OL,9,Ffilled with oily paint on the roadside
OL,10,Fin Dorset.
OL,12,FSeveral large containers were found on
OL,13,Fthe edge of the carriageway of the A35
OL,14,Fnear Bloxworth and Morden.
OL,16,FThe liquid, believed to be an oil-
OL,17,Fbased paint, had leaked from the
OL,18,Fcontainers and spread along the edge
OL,19,Fof road and into the drainage channel.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
