OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776359147
OL,3,COily paint leaks onto road after fly-
OL,4,Ctippers dump containers in Dorset
OL,6,FThe council says the fly tip had
OL,7,Fcaused a complex cleanup operation
OL,8,Fand a potential risk to the local
OL,9,Fenvironment.
OL,11,FDorset Council's Highways and Waste
OL,12,Fteams have been working to clear the
OL,13,Fwaste, with temporary traffic lights
OL,14,Fput in place to allow specialist
OL,15,Fcontractors to access the area.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
