PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776359147
OL,3,COily paint leaks onto road after fly-
OL,4,Ctippers dump containers in Dorset
OL,6,FAs of Wednesday (15 April) the council
OL,7,Fsaid it had cleared just under half of
OL,8,Fthe dumped substance from the road,
OL,9,Fwith spill kits deployed to contain
OL,10,Fthe remaining liquid and prevent it
OL,11,Fspreading.
OL,13,FIt is believed it is not linked to
OL,14,F"normal household recycling activity"
OL,15,Fas the containers are not household
OL,16,Fwaste and would not be accepted at any
OL,17,Fhousehold recycling centre.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
