PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776359147
OL,3,COily paint leaks onto road after fly-
OL,4,Ctippers dump containers in Dorset
OL,6,FThe council says the cost of dealing
OL,7,Fwith the waste is expected to be
OL,8,F"significant" and will come out of
OL,9,Ftaxpayers' money if those responsible
OL,10,Fcannot be identified.
OL,12,FDorset Council is now looking for
OL,13,Fthose involved and is encouraging
OL,14,Fanyone with information to get in
OL,15,Ftouch.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
