PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776359147
OL,3,COily paint leaks onto road after fly-
OL,4,Ctippers dump containers in Dorset
OL,6,FCllr Jon Andrews, Dorset Council's
OL,7,FCabinet Member for Place Services,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is a serious flytipping
OL,9,Fincident that has caused disruption on
OL,10,Fa key route and requires specialist
OL,11,Fwork to clear up safely.
OL,13,F"Our priority is to deal with the
OL,14,Fwaste responsibly and protect the
OL,15,Flocal environment, but we are also
OL,16,Fkeen to identify who is responsible.
