OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776359147
OL,3,COily paint leaks onto road after fly-
OL,4,Ctippers dump containers in Dorset
OL,6,F"If anyone saw vehicles stopping along
OL,7,Fthis stretch of the A35, or noticed
OL,8,Fanything unusual around the time the
OL,9,Fwaste was dumped, I would urge them to
OL,10,Fcontact us.
OL,12,F"Information from the public can play
OL,13,Fa vital role in helping us take
OL,14,Faction."
